<template>
  <cus-wraper>
    <cus-page-title-back :label="$t('i18nView.feeControlCalcFormulaDef')" @backTo="back"></cus-page-title-back>
    <cus-form-title :first="true" :label="$t('i18nView.ppCalcFormulaSelect')"></cus-form-title>
    <el-form ref="productBnftForm" :disabled="true" label-width="auto">
      <el-row :gutter="10">
        <el-col :span="8">
          <el-form-item :label="$t('i18nView.payControlType')">
            <el-tag type="info">{{ pdtempClmCtrlMain.pdBnftCtrlType | filter_clmCtrlType }}</el-tag>
          </el-form-item>
        </el-col>
        <el-col :span="8">
          <el-form-item :label="$t('i18nView.controlCode')">
            <el-tag type="info">{{ pdtempClmCtrlMain.pdBnftCtrlCode }}</el-tag>
          </el-form-item>
        </el-col>
        <el-col :span="8">
          <el-form-item :label="$t('i18nView.CalcFormulaType')">
            <el-tag type="info">{{ pdBussDetailType | filter_pdBussDetailType }}</el-tag>
          </el-form-item>
        </el-col>
      </el-row>
    </el-form>
    <el-button dialog-disable="disable" icon="el-icon-connection" size="small" type="primary" @click="toFormulaSelect">
      {{ $t('pdtempPdClmBnft.chooseExpression') }}
    </el-button>
    <cus-table-title :label="$t('pdtempPdClmBnft.expression')"/>
    <el-table :data="tableData_formula" border highlight-current-row size="mini">
      <el-table-column :label="$t('table.select')" width="50">
        <template slot-scope="scope">
          <el-radio-group v-model="selectedFormula" @change="selectedFormulaChanged(scope.row.pdCalcCode)">
            <el-radio :label="scope.row">{{ '' }}</el-radio>
          </el-radio-group>
        </template>
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('table.detail')" align="center"  width="100">
        <template slot-scope="scope">
          <el-button dialog-disable="disable" size="small" type="text" @click="showFormula(scope.row)">>></el-button>
        </template>
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('pdtempPdClmBnft.ExpressionType')" align="center"
                       prop="pdtempPdCalc.pdBussDetailType">
        <template v-slot="scope">
          {{ scope.row.pdBussDetailType | filter_pdBussDetailType }}
        </template>
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('pdtempPdClmBnft.expressionCode')" align="center" prop="pdCalcCode">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('pdtempPdClmBnft.expressionDesc')" align="center" prop="pdCalcDesc">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column align="center" :label="$t('rule.ruleAttr')">
        <template v-slot="scope">
          {{
            scope.row.ruleAttr === '1' ? $t('rule.general') : (scope.row.ruleAttr === '2' ? $t('rule.individual') : '')
          }}
        </template>
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('table.actions')" align="center" fixed="right" width="150">
        <template slot-scope="scope">
          <cus-del-btn v-auth="'clmCtrlFormula:delete'" @ok="deleteFormula(scope.row)"></cus-del-btn>
        </template>
      </el-table-column>
    </el-table>
    <cus-pagination ref="page" v-model="tableData_formula" :autoBuild="false" :pageSize="10"
                    :params="params" url="/combo-claim-compensation/base/allAssociatedFormula"/>

    <!-- 公式查看和决策树编辑弹窗 -->
    <cus-rule-modify :flag="formulaView.flag" :performType="formulaView.performType" :ruleCode="formulaView.ruleCode"
                     :ruleModifyClosed="formulaViewClosed" :ruleType="'2'"
                     :visible="formulaView.visible"></cus-rule-modify>

  </cus-wraper>
</template>

<script>

import {deleteFormula} from "@/api/basicinfo/compensationDefinition"

let _this

export default {
  name: 'clmCtrlFormula',
  props: {
    pdtempClmCtrlMain: {
      type: Object,
      required: true
    },
    pdBussDetailType: {
      type: String,
      required: true
    }
  },
  filters: {
    filter_pdBussDetailType(code) {
      return _this.getCodeName('ruleBusinessDetailClass', code)
    },
    filter_clmCtrlType(code) {
      return _this.getCodeName('clmCtrlType', code)
    }
  },
  data() {
    _this = this
    return {
      params: {
        pdBussCode: ''
      },
      tableData_formula: [],
      selectedFormula: {},
      // 产品信息
      combo: {},
      formulaView: {
        flag: '',
        ruleCode: '',
        performType: '',
        visible: false
      }
    }
  },
  created() {
    this.initProductInfo()
  },
  mounted() {
    this.initTableData()
  },
  methods: {
    initTableData() {
      this.params = {
        pdBussCode: this.pdtempClmCtrlMain.pdBnftCtrlCode
      };
      this.$nextTick(() => {
        this.$refs.page.buildData()
      })
    },
    showFormula(row) {
      this.formulaView.flag = '1'
      this.formulaView.performType = row.performType
      this.formulaView.ruleCode = row.pdCalcCode
      this.formulaView.visible = true
    },
    formulaViewClosed() {
      this.formulaView.visible = false
      this.selectedFormula = {}
    },
    initProductInfo() {
      let pdtempPdInfo = this.getPdData();
      if (Object.keys(pdtempPdInfo).length > 0) {
        Object.assign(this.combo, pdtempPdInfo)
      } else {
        this.notifyError('无法获取套餐信息')
      }
    },
    back() {
      this.$emit('changeDialogVisible_ClmCtrlFormula', false)
    },
    toFormulaSelect() {
      this.$emit('changeDialogVisible_ClmCtrlFormulaSelect', true, 'aaa')
    },
    selectedFormulaChanged() {
      this.formulaView.flag = this.selectedFormula.ruleAttr === '1' ? '1' : '2'
      this.formulaView.ruleCode = this.selectedFormula.pdCalcCode
      this.formulaView.performType = this.selectedFormula.performType
      this.formulaView.visible = true
    },
    deleteFormula(row) {
      deleteFormula(row).then(() => {
        this.notifySuccess(this.$t('successMessage.delete'))
        this.$refs.page.reload()
        this.$emit('bringInCalcCode', row.pdBussCode, undefined)
      })
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>

</style>
